# This profile is designed for Drop-CSTM80.
#
# The physical key `f13` is mapped to `LAG` (left alt + left gui).
# The physical key `right gui` is mapped to `Hyper` (left control + shift + alt + gui).
# The physical key `right alt` is mapped to `Meh` (left control + shift + alt).
# The physical key `right ctrl` is mapped to `LCAG` (left control + alt + gui).

.shell "/bin/dash"

# LAG

alt + cmd - b : open -a Zen
alt + cmd - c : open -a "Visual Studio Code"
alt + cmd - f : open -a Finder
alt + cmd - m : open -a Spotify
alt + cmd - t : open -a kitty
alt + cmd - w : open -a WhatsApp

# NOTE: At this layer, skhd reads `print_screen` as `f13`.
alt + cmd - f13 : open -a "Activity Monitor"
